'''Tahirikishimarumi no Kami''' (多比理岐志麻流美神, タヒリキシマルミ) is a deity mentioned in {{ill|Japanese mythology|ja|日本神話|qq=draft|qq=draft}}.


{{ill|Mikemunushi-no-Hiko-no-Kami|ja|甕主日子神|1=Mikemunushi-no-Hiko-no-Kami|simple|User:Immanuelle/Mikemunushi-no-Hiko-no-Kami|qq=draft|qq=draft}} was his father. This god married {{ill|Hinarashibime|ja|比那良志毘売|simple|User:Immanuelle/Hinarashibime|qq=draft|qq=draft}} (daughter of {{ill|Kuraokami|ja|淤加美神|simple|User:Immanuelle/Kuraokami|en|qq=draft|qq=draft}}) and had {{ill|Tahirikishimarumi Kami|ja|多比理岐志麻流美神|1=Tahiriki-Shimarumi-no-Kami|10=zh|11=多比理岐志麻流美神|1=Tahiriki-Shimarumi-no-Kami|simple|User:Immanuelle/Tahirikishimarumi Kami|qq=draft|qq=draft}}.

This god married {{ill|Ikutamatakitamahime Kami|ja|活玉前玉比売神|simple|User:Immanuelle/Ikutamatakitamahime Kami|qq=draft|qq=draft}} (daughter of {{ill|Hihiraginosonohanamadomi Kami|ja|比比羅木之其花麻豆美神|1=Hihiraginosonohanamadomi Kami|simple|User:Immanuelle/Hihiraginosonohanamadomi Kami|qq=draft|qq=draft}}) and had {{ill|Mironami Kami|ja|美呂浪神|simple|User:Immanuelle/Mironami Kami|qq=draft|qq=draft}}.

== Overview ==
Appearing in the genealogical record of {{ill|Ōkuninushi|ja|大国主神|qq=draft|qq=draft}} in the ''{{ill|Kojiki|ja|古事記|qq=draft|qq=draft}}'', Tahirikishimarumi no Kami is described as a fifth-generation descendant of Ōkuninushi. However, the deity's name is mentioned without any associated myths or deeds, leaving its significance and etymology ambiguous. Based on the components "Tahiriki" and "Shimarumi," the name may imply a flat island and sea, but its exact meaning is uncertain.

== Genealogy ==
[[File:Ohokuninushi family tree.png|right|thumb|250px|Genealogy of Ōkuninushi (from the ''Kojiki''). Blue represents male deities, red represents female deities, and yellow represents deities of unknown gender.]]
Tahirikishimarumi no Kami is the child of {{ill|Mikemunushi-no-Hiko-no-Kami|ja|甕主日子神|1=Mikemunushi-no-Hiko-no-Kami|simple|User:Immanuelle/Mikemunushi-no-Hiko-no-Kami|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, the fourth-generation descendant of {{ill|Ōkuninushi|ja|大国主神|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, and {{ill|Hinarashibime|ja|比那良志毘売|simple|User:Immanuelle/Hinarashibime|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, the daughter of {{ill|Kuraokami|ja|淤加美神|simple|User:Immanuelle/Kuraokami|en|qq=draft|qq=draft}}. Tahirikishimarumi no Kami marries {{ill|Ikutamatakitamahime Kami|ja|活玉前玉比売神|simple|User:Immanuelle/Ikutamatakitamahime Kami|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, the daughter of {{ill|Hihiraginosonohanamadomi Kami|ja|比比羅木之其花麻豆美神|1=Hihiraginosonohanamadomi Kami|simple|User:Immanuelle/Hihiraginosonohanamadomi Kami|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, and has a child, {{ill|Mironami Kami|ja|美呂浪神|simple|User:Immanuelle/Mironami Kami|qq=draft|qq=draft}}.

== Shrine ==
* '''Tahika Shrine''' ({{ill|Komono|ja|菰野町|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, {{ill|Mie Prefecture|ja|三重県|qq=draft|qq=draft}})
** The main shrine dedicated to Tahirikishimarumi no Kami.

