This god married {{ill|Ikutamatakitamahime Kami|ja|活玉前玉比売神|simple|User:Immanuelle/Ikutamatakitamahime Kami|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ikutamatakitamahime Kami|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} (daughter of {{ill|Hihiraginosonohanamadomi Kami|ja|比比羅木之其花麻豆美神|1=Hihiraginosonohanamadomi Kami|simple|User:Immanuelle/Hihiraginosonohanamadomi Kami|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hihiraginosonohanamadomi Kami|13=User:Immanuelle/Hihiraginosonohanamadomi Kami|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}}) and had {{ill|Mironami Kami|ja|美呂浪神|simple|User:Immanuelle/Mironami Kami|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Mironami Kami|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}}.

== Overview ==
Appearing in the genealogical record of {{ill|Ōkuninushi|ja|大国主神|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ōkuninushi|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 大国主}} in the ''[[:en:Kojiki|Kojiki]]'', Tahirikishimarumi no Kami is described as a fifth-generation descendant of Ōkuninushi. However, the deity's name is mentioned without any associated myths or deeds, leaving its significance and etymology ambiguous. Based on the components "Tahiriki" and "Shimarumi," the name may imply a flat island and sea, but its exact meaning is uncertain.

== Genealogy ==
[[File:Ohokuninushi family tree.png|right|thumb|250px|Genealogy of Ōkuninushi (from the ''Kojiki''). Blue represents male deities, red represents female deities, and yellow represents deities of unknown gender.]]
Tahirikishimarumi no Kami is the child of {{ill|Mikemunushi-no-Hiko-no-Kami|ja|甕主日子神|1=Mikemunushi-no-Hiko-no-Kami|simple|User:Immanuelle/Mikemunushi-no-Hiko-no-Kami|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Mikemunushi-no-Hiko-no-Kami|13=User:Immanuelle/Mikemunushi-no-Hiko-no-Kami|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}}, the fourth-generation descendant of {{ill|Ōkuninushi|ja|大国主神|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ōkuninushi|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 大国主}}, and {{ill|Hinarashibime|ja|比那良志毘売|simple|User:Immanuelle/Hinarashibime|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hinarashibime|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}}, the daughter of [[:en:Kuraokami|Kuraokami]]. Tahirikishimarumi no Kami marries {{ill|Ikutamatakitamahime Kami|ja|活玉前玉比売神|simple|User:Immanuelle/Ikutamatakitamahime Kami|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ikutamatakitamahime Kami|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}}, the daughter of {{ill|Hihiraginosonohanamadomi Kami|ja|比比羅木之其花麻豆美神|1=Hihiraginosonohanamadomi Kami|simple|User:Immanuelle/Hihiraginosonohanamadomi Kami|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hihiraginosonohanamadomi Kami|13=User:Immanuelle/Hihiraginosonohanamadomi Kami|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}}, and has a child, {{ill|Mironami Kami|ja|美呂浪神|simple|User:Immanuelle/Mironami Kami|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Mironami Kami|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}}.

== Shrine ==
* '''Tahika Shrine''' ([[:en:Komono|Komono]], [[:en:Mie Prefecture|Mie Prefecture]])
** The main shrine dedicated to Tahirikishimarumi no Kami.

